{"tid":1805994,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"2019 全球銷售額低於預期　華為：生存是首要任務","createTime":"2020-01-01T04:16:04.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-01T09:21:00.000Z","uid":66087,"like":8,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"647e98f54bd3deeea8e618a3809006662a1166f3","tid":1805994,"uid":66087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T04:16:04.000Z","msg":"大紀元時報<br />\n2019 年 12 月 31 日<br />\n<br />\n在中國電信巨擘華為（Huawei）宣布今年銷售因受到美國制裁影響，預估 2019 年的銷售收入將低於預期之後，華為公司副董事長暨輪值董事長徐直軍今天（31 日）表示，「生存」是首要任務。<br />\n<br />\n華為 2019 年的全球銷售額達到 8,500 億人民幣（1,210 億美元），儘管比去年增長高達 18%，但仍然遠低於原先預期的1,250 億美元。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.notebookcheck.net/fileadmin/Notebooks/News/_nc3/108868318_e032f609_60d2_4b2f_ae90_e8ea74df53f2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.notebookcheck.net%2Ffileadmin%2FNotebooks%2FNews%2F_nc3%2F108868318_e032f609_60d2_4b2f_ae90_e8ea74df53f2.jpg&h=d5351db5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n徐直軍在給員工的新年賀詞說，美國政府正處於針對華為的「戰略性和長期」運動之中，將對華為的「生存和繁榮」構成挑戰。徐直軍說，2020 年「生存將是我們的首要任務」。<br />\n<br />\n他說，華為必須「全力以赴」，以建立獨立的手機作業系統，以「確保我們能夠繼續在海外銷售我們的智慧型手機」。華為建立行動服務系統，是為回應先前搜尋引擎 Google 遵從美國禁令，終止與華為合作。"},{"pid":"6ed439e1c641bd7bf33a156afe3b3b5d5918a113","tid":1805994,"uid":69841,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T04:18:26.000Z","msg":"正一曱甴"},{"pid":"3246c8ba088540f2084b9f866474cbf17b7e94f9","tid":1805994,"uid":66087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T05:31:46.000Z","msg":"維園見 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d85d77836a3ef13d63dbe70560a3a3536c6b1ec","tid":1805994,"uid":66087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T06:39:54.000Z","msg":"到左未? <img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"